    <section class="about-hero">
        <div class="about-hero-content">
            <h1>About MelbaSolution Digital Agency</h1>
            <p>At MelbaSolution, we’re passionate about helping local businesses thrive in the digital age. We create smart, affordable digital solutions that turn your business website into your best salesperson.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-story">
        <div class="section-container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2>Our Story</h2>
                <p>Founded with a mission to bridge the gap between local businesses and global opportunities</p>
            </div>
            <div class="story-content">
                <p>MelbaSolution started simply — by helping my wife launch her shopping business online with a custom e-commerce website and mobile app. That first step showed us the power of technology for small, local businesses.</p>
                <p>
                    We saw a gap: many local businesses struggle to compete with large companies that dominate the market, simply because they lack a strong online presence. Our mission became clear — to bridge that gap by creating modern, user-friendly websites and digital tools designed to grow local businesses and keep the community thriving.
                  </p>
                  <p>
                    We are driven by customer obsession and a commitment to your growth. Whether you run a boutique, café, salon, or any local business, we’re here to create your best digital salesperson — a website that works hard for you and your customers, all at a price that makes sense.
                  </p>
                  <p>Our team combines years of experience in web development, digital marketing, and brand strategy to deliver comprehensive solutions that transform businesses from local players into global competitors.
                  </p>
                  <p>
                    Ready to take your business to the next level? Let’s talk. Explore our services and discover how MelbaSolution can help you grow and succeed in today’s digital world.
                  </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="values">
        <div class="section-container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2>Our Values</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="values-grid">
                <div class="value-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i>
                    <h3>Innovation</h3>
                    <p>We stay ahead of digital trends to provide cutting-edge solutions.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="value-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-handshake"></i>
                    <h3>Partnership</h3>
                    <p>We work as your trusted partner, not just a service provider.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="value-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
                    <h3>Results</h3>
                    <p>We focus on measurable outcomes that drive business growth.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="value-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
                    <h3>Collaboration</h3>
                    <p>We believe in transparent communication and collaborative processes.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="value-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-globe"></i>
                    <h3>Global Reach</h3>
                    <p>We help local businesses expand their presence to international markets.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="value-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-rocket"></i>
                    <h3>Growth</h3>
                    <p>We accelerate business transformation through strategic digital solutions.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

